Run
/ PLang entry point — routes to build, test, or run based on CLI parameters
- if %!build%, call Build
- if %!test%, call RunTests
- read file %goalFile%, write to %goals%
- foreach %goals%, call RunGoal, item=%goal%

RunGoal
/ Executes a single goal's steps
- foreach %goal.Steps%, call RunStep, item=%step%

RunStep
/ Dispatches a single step via the kernel
- execute %step%, write to %result%
